snippet.textDisplay:
Fellow Smash players please listen carefuly to my wording. I understand why you are upset, but this was to be expected. FE is at its greatest right now. Three Houses was rated the second best game by both critics and players of 2019, it was also voted as a game that should have been at least mentioned as a possibility for best game of the year awards by the players. Byleth was a character who was a major role in a series unlike characters like Waluigi (who think is a awesome character), was made by people willing to let their character be in smash unlike the Cloud from Square Enix who was barely added, and was a character everyone would know. Just give Sakurai a break and stop yelling bloody murder! Many characters can be chosen but only few are a fit.
(Hollow Knight I hope will get a spot.)

1:17 She could have said that to anybody!
I will say, i hated this character for like an hour after I saw the whole thing. After hearing all the criticism and hateful comments towards Sakurai, it's really just ridiculous, like who cares, it's just another character to play as. I for one don't really care about the character, because all I wanted was to see the final character of the first fighters pass, and after seeing who is, play the character regardless whether or not I know them or not because I play this game for the battles.
I have a phrase for this tho,

At the end of the day, it doesn't matter who the character is, what matters is how they play in the game.

I want all the haters to know this so they would stop shaming Sakurai for just putting a character in smash.
To them, i say:🖕🏾 u
To Sakurai, i say: You're the man.
